name: Nomen Luni - Part 6 of the Frag Fest series!
description: I was promising something special for Frag Fest 6, and here you have it. Not quite what it started out as, but after playing GIGAKIL2 by Stealth (respect due, some amazing levels...) I was duely inpired by his ISLEKEEP level, and created this, totally unlike it, except for the sea-side idea.
